1.3 ~ May 11th, 2013
	- Fixed calculator styling in Firefox
	- Some minor style changes/additions
	- Added more comments
	- Allowed decimal points in the diagonal measurement input field
	- Added close icon to the presets menu
	- Added -prefix-free for styling

